{"tid":1491052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪應該係六大訴求？","createTime":"2019-08-20T09:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T19:31:00.000Z","uid":172602,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2c53a6eeff8705670eac992c555ba268b1edb40e","tid":1491052,"uid":172602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:34:00.000Z","msg":"其實好多人 包括我在內一路嘅口號都係 <br />\n「五大訴求 缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n但係721之後其實有人提過 加埋徹查警黑勾結<br />\n當然唔係嗌下就可以實現 但唔知點解無咗件事<br />\n但呢個月 其實一直發生緊針對抗爭者/無差別傷人<br />\n係咪應該正式將警黑勾結/緝拿真。兇徒歸案<br />\n（拉咗就煮重佢地米 唔好畀DOJ咁易放人）<br />\n<br />\n同原本嘅五大訴求並列為<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">六大訴求</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集思廣益 我認為呢點幾重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463f4c90d5838fbbdf70a72189ffebcf9c86fe37","tid":1491052,"uid":34154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:34:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">六大訴求 缺一不可<br />\nAll six demands must be met</span></span>"},{"pid":"3b65cbb8b3713d523a35007d941e8ad10e667238","tid":1491052,"uid":69334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:35:37.000Z","msg":"六大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"17048e6d1104dd55991c24e4374a69731dcd8d37","tid":1491052,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"我覺得係解散警隊，全面改革"},{"pid":"b2b3d8a1fdb9a88ffb1578409f3a053e0bfc9ca3","tid":1491052,"uid":34088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafb2e6cbde04076d75e2f96bf91ef55a3c99d99","tid":1491052,"uid":102491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"唔好講推 將所有核彈列明黎推post<br />\n歡迎增加任用<br />\n<br />\n置頂 曱甴論+動用私刑+日日講大話！<br />\n1. 射頭<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 無啦啦拘捕個女人<br />\n5. 室內開槍<br />\n6. 過份使用武力+催淚彈<br />\n7. 冇委任證<br />\n8. 過期催淚彈<br />\n9. 警黑勾結<br />\n10. 無差別濫捕<br />\n11. 光明正大講大話<br />\n12. 誣蔑市民+陷害市民<br />\n13. 拆證物<br />\n14. 無視任何法律及指引<br />\n15. 葉虎事件<br />\n16. 因應政見決定做野同起訴速度<br />\n<br />\n佢地搞到香港咁樣 人人都生意差冇工開佢地仲計ot幾萬蚊準時出糧一定唔驚，諗計斷班撚樣既飯碗<br />\n香港人唔再需要唔保護市民既警察！！唔想再出糧俾一啲開槍打我 用棍扑我既人 清算黑警<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求"},{"pid":"bfe80b813e4f615df14cec94c431f090ec457983","tid":1491052,"uid":172602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17048e6d1104dd55991c24e4374a69731dcd8d37","tid":1491052,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"我覺得係解散警隊，全面改革"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:43:50.000Z","msg":"都得 我覺得呢個係獨立調查嘅加強版<br />\n題外話 我都唔知林鄭下台係咪五大訴求之一<br />\n有時話係有時話唔係"},{"pid":"b3aa6196f836765ac418d17bdd6dda03e9ecdf98","tid":1491052,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfe80b813e4f615df14cec94c431f090ec457983","tid":1491052,"uid":172602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17048e6d1104dd55991c24e4374a69731dcd8d37","tid":1491052,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"我覺得係解散警隊，全面改革"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:43:50.000Z","msg":"都得 我覺得呢個係獨立調查嘅加強版<br />\n題外話 我都唔知林鄭下台係咪五大訴求之一<br />\n有時話係有時話唔係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:59:15.000Z","msg":"林鄭既然匿響警隊後面，當然要佢冇地方匿！"},{"pid":"47e7327af9f5604bc6e86668207e6eceb9d249cb","tid":1491052,"uid":165665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"幾時港獨？"},{"pid":"9e7ac5e6b70df06531ba7737fb966ec839b5d310","tid":1491052,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:06:12.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 紅色綠豆 )"},{"pid":"2584e97c9ed29356d455ed36aaa6453c3317dc56","tid":1491052,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:53:3